1.0.0.name: wordpress/_second-foundation
1.0.0.description: _Second Foundation is a highly customizable theme featuring full page image backgrounds, AJAX menus, Masonry and many mobile-friendly features. Thanks to the Foundation framework it adapts to any size screen and even serves smaller images for smaller devices to improve page load times on mobile.
